snippet.title: D Billions LIVE SHOW! A Billion Smiles! | Bishkek 2023! Chicky, Cha-Cha, Boom-Boom, Lya-Lya & More!
snippet.description:
https://band.link/DBillions

Hello, everyone! We have fantastic news! Our world tour has just begun and today we want to show you our first concert which took place in Bishkek, the capital of Kyrgyz Republic. With the support from nonprofit organization "Ene Balaga Tirek" we were able to gather over 40 thousand people! We saw joy and happy smiles on faces of thousands of kids. They had an opportunity to see their favorite characters live! Dear friends, where would you like to see us next?

Happy watching!

snippet.title: Exploring the World! Cha-Cha, Lya-Lya & Boom-Boom are Visiting Vietnam | D Billions' Travels
snippet.description:
Hello friends! We are introducing you to D Billions' Travel adventures! Get ready for an unforgettable adventure at the amazing Amusement Park in the heart of Vietnam! Together with Cha-Cha, Lya-Lya and Boom-Boom, you will walk along the paths of the park, feel the adrenaline from high-speed rides, meet unusual animals - from colorful birds to cute camels and giant rhinos! Also, the mysterious world of the aquarium awaits you, where you will learn amazing facts about the diversity of aquatic life!
